#######
#ingame
#######

^#5aa9d6;Adds the Manufacturer's Touch options to Grand Armory weapons.^reset;

This mod is an optional patch, but requires Manufacturer's Touch and Grand Armory to work.
For now precludes bows and spellbooks.

For more, click the MEGATHREAD link from the steam page.

######
#steam
######

[h1]Adds the Manufacturer's Touch options to Grand Armory weapons.[/h1]

This mod is an optional patch, but requires [url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=760396113]Manufacturer's Touch[/url] and [url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=836238594]Grand Armory[/url] to work.
For now precludes bows and spellbooks.

[url=community.playstarbound.com/threads/124193/]MEGATHREAD[/url]
Alternate downloads can be found on my [url=https://github.com/IsaacHart/sbcom-grandarm-mt/releases/0.3/]github.[/url]

