#forum
######

Adds the Manufacturer's Touch options to Grand Armory weapons.

This mod is an optional patch, but requires [url=community.playstarbound.com/resources/4095/]Manufacturer's Touch[/url] and [url=community.playstarbound.com/resources/4430/]Grand Armory[/url] to work.
